## Loading Performance

### Image Optimization

| Image Type | Format | Max Size | Optimization |
|------------|--------|----------|--------------|
| Hero/banner | WebP with JPEG fallback | 200 KB | Responsive srcset |
| Thumbnails | WebP | 30 KB | Fixed dimensions |
| Icons | SVG (inline or sprite) | 5 KB | Minified |
| Photographs | WebP/AVIF | 100 KB per breakpoint | Progressive loading |

```html
<!-- Responsive image with lazy loading -->
<img
  srcset="image-400.webp 400w, image-800.webp 800w, image-1200.webp 1200w"
  sizes="(max-width: 600px) 400px, (max-width: 1000px) 800px, 1200px"
  src="image-800.webp"
  alt="Descriptive alt text"
  loading="lazy"
  decoding="async"
  width="800"
  height="600"
/>
```

### Code Splitting

- [ ] Route-based code splitting (dynamic imports for each route)
- [ ] Component-level splitting for heavy components (charts, editors)
- [ ] Vendor chunk separation (node_modules isolated)
- [ ] No single chunk exceeds 150 KB gzipped

```typescript
// Route-level splitting
const Dashboard = lazy(() => import('./pages/Dashboard'));

// Component-level splitting
const ChartWidget = lazy(() => import('./components/ChartWidget'));
```

### Resource Loading Priority

| Resource | Priority | Strategy |
|----------|----------|----------|
| Critical CSS | Highest | Inline in `<head>` |
| Main JS bundle | High | `<script>` with preload |
| Web fonts | High | `font-display: swap` + preload |
| Below-fold images | Low | `loading="lazy"` |
| Analytics | Low | `defer` or `async` |
| Third-party widgets | Lowest | Lazy load on interaction |

