## Network Performance

### API Request Budgets

| Request Type | Target Latency | Max Payload |
|--------------|----------------|-------------|
| Page data fetch | < 200ms | 50 KB |
| Search/filter | < 300ms | 100 KB |
| Form submission | < 500ms | 10 KB |
| File upload | Progress indicator | Chunked |

### Caching Strategy

| Resource | Cache Duration | Strategy |
|----------|---------------|----------|
| Static assets (JS, CSS) | 1 year | Fingerprinted filenames |
| API responses | Varies | stale-while-revalidate |
| Images | 1 month | CDN with versioning |
| HTML | No cache | Server-rendered fresh |

